      "NO NO NO! Cleanly please!! K-drama villains are CRYING right now!! Again!!",
      "AIGOO 친구야!! 그 발음 뭐야?! My ears are BLEEDING!! 한 번 더!! Speak!!",
      "YAH!! 진짜?! That was BOLD!! BOLD AND WRONG!! Copy me — 다시!!",
